Description: Assess Water Quality Trends for Long-Term Monitoring Data in Estuaries 
  using Generalized Additive Models and Error Propagation with Mixed-Effects Meta-Analysis. Methods
  are available for model fitting, assessment of fit, annual and seasonal trend tests, and 
  visualization of results.
